name: Send Email
script:
bh.status = 200; bh.payload = { to: bh.input.body.email, subject: 'Dead Or Alive Client Registered', from: 'DOAServices', ptag: `

Your registration with DOA was successful.

Your Email to login is: ${bh.input.body.email}

Your Password to login is: ${bh.sendPassword}

PLEASE CLICK THE IMAGE BELOW TO VIEW PLAN

` }
